		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64715532"><p>In Norway several chains use e-ink price tags, and raising prices only happens outside of opening hours. Lowering prices can happen at any time.</p><p>Sure, requires the stores to play ball but it&#226;(TM)s a good principle. If stores fuck around, legislation will easily harmonise behavior so as to protect consumers.</p></div>
